kaadu &lt;unk&gt; neram is a 2016 indian malayalam drama film written and directed by dr. biju . the film stars indrajith sukumaran , bharath gopi , narain , rima kallingal and bharath gopi in the lead roles . the film tells the story of three people living in the state of kerala . the film stars indrajith sukumaran , bharath gopi , samuthirakani , rima kallingal and bharath gopi in the lead roles . the film was released on 6 january 2016 .